<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <title>BABATHE.COM - 상품상세</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="../../css/library.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="../../css/common.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="../../css/templateA.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="../../css/templateB.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="../../css/templateC.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="../../css/templateD.css">
    <script src="../../js/swiper-bundle.min.js"></script>
    <script src="../../js/layout.js"></script>
</head>
<body class="goodsDetail">
    <header>
        <div class="sub-hedaer">
            <button type="button" class="btn-back">뒤로가기</button>
            <h1 class="page-title">이벤트</h1>
            <button type="button" class="btn-search">검색</button>
            <button type="button" class="btn-cart">장바구니<span class="num">11</span></button>
        </div>
    </header>
    <section>

        <!-- contentsGroup -->
        <div class="contentsGroup" style="background: pink;padding:268px 0;text-align: center;">
            등록 컨텐츠 영역
        </div>
        <!-- //contentsGroup -->

        <!-- contentsGroup -->
        <div class="contentsGroup">

            <!-- event-detail-title -->
            <div class="event-detail-title">
                이벤트명 노출영역 최대 두줄로 길어질 경우 줄바꿈되어 노출됩니다. 글자수 제한이 필요합니다.
            </div>
            <!-- //event-detail-title -->

            <!-- event-detail-extra -->
            <div class="event-detail-title-extra">
                <div class="event-detail-date">2021-01-18 ~ 2021-01-24</div>
                <div class="event-detail-share">
                    <button class="share"><span class="for-a11y">공유하기</span></button>
                </div>
            </div>
            <!-- //event-detail-extra -->

            <!-- title-area -->
            <div class="title-area">
                <div class="title-area-inner">
                    <h3 class="title">알록달록 내가 사랑하는 컬러는?</h3>
                </div>
            </div>
            <!-- //title-area -->

            <!-- vote-type01 -->
            <div class="vote-type01">
                <div class="inner">
                    <label for="vote0101">
                        <input type="radio" class="type2" id="vote0101" name="vote01" checked>
                        <img src="../../img/temp/thumb-310x413.png" alt="">
                        <span>빨간 장미가<br>생각나는 붉은색</span>
                    </label>
                    <label for="vote0102">
                        <input type="radio" class="type2" id="vote0102" name="vote01">
                        <img src="../../img/temp/thumb-310x413.png" alt="">
                        <span>귀여운 개나리가<br>생각나는 노란색</span>
                    </label>
                    <label for="vote0103">
                        <input type="radio" class="type2" id="vote0103" name="vote01">
                        <img src="../../img/temp/thumb-310x413.png" alt="">
                        <span>새콤, 탱글탱글 감귤이<br>떠오르는 주황색</span>
                    </label>
                    <label for="vote0104">
                        <input type="radio" class="type2" id="vote0104" name="vote01">
                        <img src="../../img/temp/thumb-310x413.png" alt="">
                        <span>차분함이 느껴지는<br>매력적인 남색</span>
                    </label>
                </div>
                <div class="btnWrap">
                    <button class="btn-basicM fill">투표하기</button>
                </div>
            </div>
            <!-- //vote-type01 -->





            <!-- title-area -->
            <div class="title-area">
                <div class="title-area-inner">
                    <h3 class="title">알록달록 내가 사랑하는 컬러는?</h3>
                </div>
            </div>
            <!-- //title-area -->

            <!-- vote-type02 -->
            <div class="vote-type02">
                <ul>
                    <li>
                        <input type="radio" name="vote02" id="vote0201" checked>
                        <label for="vote0201">빨간 장미가 생각나는 붉은색</label>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <input type="radio" name="vote02" id="vote0202">
                        <label for="vote0202">귀여운 개나리가 생각나는 노란색</label>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <input type="radio" name="vote02" id="vote0203">
                        <label for="vote0203">새콤, 탱글탱글 감귤이 떠오르는 주황색</label>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <input type="radio" name="vote02" id="vote0204">
                        <label for="vote0204">차분함이 느껴지는 매력적인 남색</label>
                    </li>
                </ul>
                <div class="btnWrap">
                    <button class="btn-basicM fill">투표하기</button>
                </div>
            </div>
            <!-- //vote-type02 -->

            <!-- message-box" -->
            <div class="message-box">
                <div class="message-box-tit">쿠폰 유의사항</div>
                <div class="message-box-txt">
                    <ul class="tip-wrap">
                        <li class="tip type3">쿠폰 사용기간 내 정해진 조건충족 시 할인적용이 가능합니다.</li>
                        <li class="tip type3">쿠폰 사용 시 최소구매금액과 최대할인금액을 확인하세요.</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
            <!-- //message-box" -->







        </div>
        <!-- //contentsGroup -->


    </section>
    <footer></footer>
</body>
</html>